<br>
/brag on<br>
<br>
I play a female (and am one IRL) woodelven warrior on Sol Ro, born 3/29/99. Im an old school D&amp;D player and thought woot, heres my dream.  Didnt realize then what the 'high end' game was going to be, i was too concerned with the bat and that damn orc pawn that kept trying to eat me, and often did!<br>
<br>
Morg(anath) is currently 60th and has 6 AA points.  Once I realised where the 'end game' was going I sat down and did some hard research on skills/stats, however I never did any on 'tanking' everything I've learned I've learned by trial and error and through example by watching others (some of the best I must admit /bow Kubla /bow Baxter)  and Im still learning every time I log on<br>
<br>
Now for the /brag part.  Morg with regular gear comprised of some Skyshrine, some ToV, some Umbral, and other odd bits and pieces, armed with a Defiance/Snowchipper, with an unbuffed str 170, sta 120, agil 125, dex 150 can out-taunt/tank/whoopAss Barbs and Ogres, Trolls and Dorfs, Humans, Leezards and any class out there.  Buffed?  Holy shiznat look out!  /brag off<br>
<br>
Im very proud of my little Morg (sorry hehe just had to share all this in a world of BIG folk)<br>
<br>
So when I was directed to this site (never knew it existed) and took a look around I realised WOW I've got so much to learn.  Im absolutely drooling on much better a tank I can become!  This site rocks!!!  Thank you whomever took the time to put all this together for us 'meatshields'<br>
