     <br>
Anyways that was beside the point. After awhile though, I figured that I like getting beat on and beating back since I never really had mana or cast spells with my druid. So I created a halfling warrior, but to my dismay I created a dwarf soon afterwards. Dont get me wrong dwarfs are awesome, but if I could change my race, I'd be a halfling all the way.<br>
<br>
P.S. Dont ever quit for AO or DAoC...especially dont give your stuff away if your not sure you like those games. <br>
<br>
