On a more serious note...<br>
<br>
20% Penalty - Troll, Iksar<br>
15% Penalty - Ogre<br>
5% Penalty - Barbarian<br>
5% Bonus - Halfling<br>
<br>
Just remember all warriors have a 10% Bonus despite the fact they removed all the penalties from the other classes (Rogues also retain a 5% Bonus as well but thats a matter for another thread).<br>
<br>
I've played many warriors on TZ... Barb, Halfling, Dwarf, Wood Elf, Half Elf... all to 20, and I'll say I enjoyed my WoodElf the most, despite the lack of slam the high agi/dex meant procing weapons went off alot more and alot less damage taken by melee. <p>Slowmotionz Unstopable<br>
